Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Layer:10 LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的事实 就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音…玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我会变成真神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所认定的神绝对不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白肉体是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的意思 只是把肉体放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说千砂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这种地方 我不存在也没所谓）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说也对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让网络协议进化的更趋完整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你的确做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但协议也只是协议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已在更高层次之处加上我才知道的密码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把情报放在那资料里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样的情报呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括我和那英利政美的思想 履历 记录 情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做到底有何意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以匿名的方式存在于网络上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能永远生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能控制网上的数据 支配一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种存在方式 应该称呼为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实神是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是能以普通的方式存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在上位的话 也不能称为神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 它是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 是被做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不再需要肉体了 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 把书收进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何突然变成如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做错过什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直不敢胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但果然还是变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我真的不该拥有肉体？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这现实世界已不再需要有你存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你道别了 玲音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的工作已完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在短短的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没好好对待妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此你自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实从开始你就自由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不能跟你说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有一般家庭的融洽生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但曾是玲音父亲的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感到非常光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要留下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你不只是一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你到网络上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会有人来欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是这样子的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要做什么？玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的世界 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是否做了个假的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据东方传说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士团的起源似乎是圆桌骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在还没有互联网时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们利用人与人之间所构成的网络
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来收集所需要的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要做什么？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS…KNIGHTS到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想知道吗？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为作为计算机网络上的神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定要拥有崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到别的地方好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得这很无聊吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 要不要来我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昌幸你不来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎不会跟你这种小鬼玩的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么话 你也是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩年轻是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网络新闻说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说名单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么名单？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS成员的名单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在网络上流传
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要出声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我替他注射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈我在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个换妈妈你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快来的话我就继续玩了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈你好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要继续玩了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天世界各地出现连串自杀事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地警方正全力追查原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀身亡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据消息报导
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是网络上一个名叫KNIGHTS的组织之中的成员…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为何要这样做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是我们客户的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把全世界的KNIGHTS成员找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就负责一切善后工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上世界并非特别的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充其量只是真实世界的某部份备案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你在网上已全无存在目标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已平安无事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得你像是有守护神在保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天那英利政美残留的计算机程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要它从网络上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们那位顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要我们将那程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远消失在网络上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…不需要神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 无论现实或网上都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法了解你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可说是很不可思议的…感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些崇拜的人已不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么照你所说的 神已经不存在了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是所有人都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要还有一个崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就还是能当神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊 就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能以你所存在 都是我的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本就是网络的创造者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是网上的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网络童话的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实世界的岩仓玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个程序
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类所做出来的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本没有一个实体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假的家人 假的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 全是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的玲音 已经是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深爱着你的我还在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你送来这世界的应该是爱着你的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你的创造者
